    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Overview\r\n\r\nThis workbook helps identify and review administrative user accounts in Microsoft Entra ID, which often use identifiers like `admin` or `adm`. Since these accounts typically lack an inbox, this workbook helps bridge the gap by identifying potential contact emails from active users with similar names. It pulls data from Entra sign-in logs to facilitate auditing and improve communication with administrators.\r\n\r\nYou may need to revise the workbook's KQL queries if your naming pattern differs significantly.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Important Note on Data Scope\r\n\r\nThis workbook's analysis is based on **Microsoft Entra sign-in logs**. Therefore, it will only include administrative accounts that have been active within the selected time range of the query.\r\n\r\n**Accounts that have been idle and have no sign-in activity during that period will not appear in the results.**\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Workbook Tabs\r\n\r\n### 1. Admin Activity Review\r\n\r\nThis tab provides a dashboard for auditing admin activity. It includes widgets for:\r\n*   Authentication success and failure.\r\n*   Possible contact emails based on name matching.\r\n*   Privileged Identity Management (PIM) activity.\r\n*   Azure activity.\r\n\r\n### 2. Downloadable Admin Contact List\r\n\r\nThis tab provides a downloadable table listing all identified admins alongside potential user accounts. This list can be used to support automated or manual efforts to add contact emails to the admin user account properties in Entra ID.\r\n"
            },
            "name": "text - 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "showHelp",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "Yes"
      },
      "name": "Show Help"
    },
    {
      "type": 11,
      "content": {
        "version": "LinkItem/1.0",
        "style": "tabs",
        "tabStyle": "bigger",
        "links": [
          {
            "id": "dc877aa9-7343-437d-86fe-2b13ac8d318f",
            "cellValue": "tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Admin Review",
            "subTarget": "tab1",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "ba0c237c-39c8-4ebf-9ce4-16ddb9ca75a9",
            "cellValue": "tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Admin User Lookup",
            "subTarget": "tab2",
            "style": "link"
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "links - 2"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let adminSignins = SigninLogs\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName\r\n| where UserPrincipalName contains \"{Search}\"\r\n| extend username = tostring(split(UserPrincipalName, \"@\")[0])\r\n| extend nameParts = split(username, \".\")\r\n| extend firstName = tostring(nameParts[0])\r\n| extend lastName = tostring(nameParts[-2])\r\n| extend compare = strcat(firstName, lastName)\r\n| project Admin_UPN=UserPrincipalName, Admin_DisplayName=Identity, compare;\r\nlet nonAdminSignins = SigninLogs\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName\r\n| where UserPrincipalName !contains \"admin\"\r\n| extend username = tostring(split(UserPrincipalName, \"@\")[0])\r\n| extend nameParts = split(username, \".\")\r\n| extend firstName = tostring(nameParts[0])\r\n| extend lastName = tostring(nameParts[-2])\r\n| extend compare = strcat(firstName, lastName)\r\n| project User_UPN=UserPrincipalName, User_DisplayName=Identity, compare;\r\nadminSignins\r\n| join kind=inner (\r\nnonAdminSignins\r\n) on compare\r\n| summarize Correlated_User_UPNs = make_list(User_UPN) by Admin_UPN, Admin_DisplayName\r\n| project \r\n    Admin_DisplayName,\r\n    Admin_UPN, \r\n    Count = array_length(Correlated_User_UPNs),\r\n    Sample_User = Correlated_User_UPNs[0],\r\n    Correlated_User_UPNs",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeGenerated",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Workspace}"
              ],
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Admin_DisplayName",
                    "formatter": 0,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "customColumnWidthSetting": "30ch"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Admin_UPN",
                    "formatter": 0,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "customColumnWidthSetting": "45ch"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Sample_User",
                    "formatter": 0,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "customColumnWidthSetting": "35ch"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Correlated_User_UPNs",
                    "formatter": 0,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "customColumnWidthSetting": "35ch"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 10000,
                "filter": true
              }
            },
            "name": "query - 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "tab2"
      },
      "name": "Group2"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
